name: com.castsoftware.dmtjeefilediscoverer
title: JEE File Discoverer
description: Support for discovering java files. It should be used when the java project files are not delivered with the source code or not covered by any extension. It's a kind of "catch-all". Be aware that CAST does not recommend to use this extension since the configuration is not complete (discovery should be based on project files). You must define in CMS the options for these analysis units and the dependencies.
